==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionChangeLineAttributes''' tool changes the attributes (style, width and color) of cosmetic lines and centerlines.

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionChangeLineAttributesExample.png|300px]]
{{Caption|On the right centerlines with updated line attributes: style&#61;DashDot, width&#61;Thin and color&#61;Blue}}

==Usage==

# Optionally specify the line attributes with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select one or more cosmetic lines and/or centerlines.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionChangeLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionChangeLineAttributes|Change Line Attributes]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionChangeLineAttributes.svg|16px]] Change Line Attributes}} option from the menu.
# The attributes of the selected lines are updated.


